{
  "stem": "4753.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Because after two weeks, asking questions, you know, groups who were passing us as we were going somewhere, where we were taken somewhere to work, asking groups passing each other if they know where is my sister, asking my sister's name.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I found-- I did find out that she was in the E camp.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I wanted desperately to meet her.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] finally, I found out that the camp where I was, that was 3B, Hungarian camp.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "One side of the camp-- you know, all the camps with the barracks were surrounded with electrified wires, very tall-- I don't know, maybe nine feet tall.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I don't know exactly how tall.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But one side of our, our camp wasn't.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Because they never finished the camp.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "They never intended us to survive.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "We were not even numbered.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Because the time we came in, we were the last transp-- not la-- not the very last from Hungary, but the last country taken the people to camp were directed, directed to a gas chamber.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "What did they do or why they decided not to put us all in the oven, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "But we did go to that camp what was not finished.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And a few blocks-- I mean, a few yard, maybe 100 yard or so far, or even farther, in that side what never was finished, was three other barracks.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And that was some kind of [INAUDIBLE] called.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "I did find out that my sister is going there to work.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "But that took many, many weeks after I was in Auschwitz and hiding behind my girlfriend's back in roll calls to stay there to be able to see my sister.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And finally, when I did see her, I over to her.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] We hugged.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
